00:20:36,575 --> 00:20:37,618
cards and everything.

480
00:20:38,974 --> 00:20:40,235
And that worked out pretty well, but then we ran

481
00:20:40,255 --> 00:20:41,455
into the fact that we had a pretty small

482
00:20:41,495 --> 00:20:43,716
music budget and silent films are scored and we

483
00:20:43,736 --> 00:20:46,158
couldn't afford to score all these with custom music.

484
00:20:46,358 --> 00:20:51,540
And our, our awesome audio guys licensed classical music and

485
00:20:51,880 --> 00:20:54,562
managed to edit that to the cut scenes as

486
00:20:54,622 --> 00:20:56,222
if it were custom scored music, and it worked

487
00:20:56,302 --> 00:20:56,803
really well.

488
00:20:57,223 --> 00:20:58,724
And it was really awesome to have a

