00:20:58,764 --> 00:21:00,524
doll fart while Chopin was playing in the background,

490
00:21:00,604 --> 00:21:01,045
which was great.

491
00:21:02,300 --> 00:21:04,241
And, and ultimately this silent film stuff added more

492
00:21:04,281 --> 00:21:06,062
personality for us. It gave us another motif to

493
00:21:06,082 --> 00:21:07,363
kind of weave in with some of the

