00:21:30,268 --> 00:21:31,650
And that's not really what I'm thinking. Like, the

507
00:21:31,830 --> 00:21:34,333
idea of, we embraced our limitations and by embracing

508
00:21:34,353 --> 00:21:36,856
them we made different creative choices than we would

509
00:21:36,877 --> 00:21:38,979
have otherwise made. And that went a long ways

510
00:21:39,019 --> 00:21:42,143
to giving the game its own sense of personality.

511
00:21:42,183 --> 00:21:44,586
So just work with those limitations. It's probably gonna

512
00:21:44,626 --> 00:21:46,288
come out pretty cool. Like, most, everyone in this

513
00:21:46,308 --> 00:21:47,069
industry is really clever.

514
00:21:48,589 --> 00:21:49,989
And then find your essence early.

515
00:21:50,750 --> 00:21:53,551
I think the amnesia Fortnite process forces you to,

516
00:21:53,731 --> 00:21:55,632
forces you in a very fatherly good way,

517
00:21:55,932 --> 00:21:59,134
to find all of the personality up front.

518
00:21:59,554 --> 00:22:00,955
Don't just prototype the core mechanic

519
00:22:00,995 --> 00:22:01,735
in the gray box world.

