00:23:18,903 --> 00:23:24,107
We need to rewind all the way back to a time when housing prices could only go up and when

552
00:23:24,207 --> 00:23:27,010
cutting edge internet humor was Rick Rolling and LOLcats.

553
00:23:27,030 --> 00:23:29,392
And by that I mean the amazing year of 2007.

